title: [Caffe2] Follow-up of onnx-trt API change
body_html:
Recent refactoring of onnx-trt code (https://github.com/thatguymike/onnx-trt/pull/19) has changed its API. This PR makes corresponding changes to followup.

In addition, it changes the way we skip tests by looking at the pybind module attribute, which follows our convention.
